* v0.3-3
* Added a reload.project() function.
* Improved error handling.
* Renamed utilities.R to helpers.R.
* Fixed a bug in cache().

2011-06-27	John Myles White  <jmw@johnmyleswhite.com>
 
* v0.3-2
